{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow families to have Christmas day together in all tiers",
        "additional_details": "Christmas is very special to majority of people and especially this year, we want to spend time with our loved ones. Just one day for all tiers to spend with their family, either 2 or 3 households and them back to full lockdown on boxing day. \r\n\r\nSome people who are key workers have no choice but to keep working and Christmas Day is the right time to spend quality time with your family",
        "background": "Allow families up to 3 households to be able to spend time with their loved ones for just one day on Christmas day, no matter what the tier.",
